《'''火线重案组'''》（{{lang-en|''The Wire''}}），又译为《'''火线'''》、《'''监听风云'''》。是一部[[美国|美国]][[犯罪片|犯罪]][[电视剧|电视剧]]，讲述了[[马里兰州|马里兰州]][[巴尔的摩市|巴尔的摩市]]警察与犯罪团伙间交锋的故事。全剧在巴尔的摩市实地取景，采用单机摄制（film-style shooting）。前罪案记者、作家[[大卫·西蒙_(作家)|大卫·西蒙]]担任本片的制片人兼领衔编剧。全剧由[[有线电视|有线电视]]网[[HBO|HBO]]在美国播出，于2002年6月2日首播，2008年3月9日完结，共5季60集。

《火线》的每季集中表现巴尔的摩市的-{zh-cn:一个侧面; zh-tw:側寫;}-。按照播出季顺序依次为：[[毒品|毒品]]交易、[[港口|港口]]众生、[[官僚主义|官僚主义]]作风的市政府、无能的教育系统及平面媒体。本片起用了众多并不出名的性格演员。西蒙曾说过，尽管这是一部犯罪类剧情剧，但全剧“实际上是在讲美国城市，在讲我们如何共同生活。是要向观众展现群体对个体的影响，无论你是警察、码头工人、毒贩、政客、法官或是律师，你最终都必须妥协，效忠自己所属的群体”<ref name="TAR">{{cite video|people = David Simon|year = 2005|language = en
|title = "The Target" commentary track|medium = DVD|publisher = [[HBO|HBO]]}}</ref>。

尽管没有获得巨大的商业成功，也没有赢得主流的电视奖项<ref name="HBO-2004-Wire">{{cite web|author = David Simon|year = 2004|title = Ask ''The Wire'': David Simon|publisher = [[HBO|HBO]]|language = en|accessdate = |url = http://boards.hbo.com/click.jspa?searchID=-1&messageID=100296266|archive-date = 2007-05-16|archive-url = https://archive.today/20070516134111/http://boards.hbo.com/click.jspa?searchID=-1&messageID=100296266|dead-url = yes}}</ref>，但《火线》依然得到了评论界的广泛好评，常被视为是有史以来最伟大的电视剧<ref name="greatest">{{cite web|url=http://www.salon.com/ent/tv/feature/2007/09/15/best_show|title=The best TV show of all time|date=2007-09-15|last=Traister|first=Rebbeca|language=en|accessdate=2008-03-07|publisher=Salon.com|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090930225528/http://www.salon.com/ent/tv/feature/2007/09/15/best_show/|archivedate=2009-09-30}}</ref><ref name="metascore1">{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/shows/wireseason4?q=the%20wire|title=Wire, The Season 4|accessdate=2008-03-07|language=en|publisher=MetaCritic|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080221022558/http://www.metacritic.com/tv/shows/wireseason4?q=the%20wire|archivedate=2008-02-21}}</ref><ref name="metascore2">{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/shows/wireseason5?q=the%20wire|title=Wire, The Season 5|accessdate=2008-03-07|language=en|publisher=MetaCritic|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080913234854/http://www.metacritic.com/tv/shows/wireseason5?q=the%20wire|archivedate=2008-09-13}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/5095500/The-Wire-arguably-the-greatest-television-programme-ever-made.html|title=The Wire: arguably the greatest television programme ever made|date=2009-04-02|language=en|work=Telegraph|accessdate=2009-04-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090404044444/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/5095500/The-Wire-arguably-the-greatest-television-programme-ever-made.html|archivedate=2009-04-04}}</ref><ref name="guardian1"