== 演员及角色 ==
《火线》拥有庞大的常规演出阵容，此外众多客串角色。本剧演员中[[非裔美国人|非裔美国人]]所占比重较大，这准确的反映了巴尔的摩市的人口构成，但在美国电视剧中十分罕见。2008年2月3日，本剧第55集播出，这使得《火线》在以黑人为主要演出阵容的电视剧中，播出集数仅次于《灵魂食物》（Soul Food），位列第二。

该剧的创作者还敢于让主要角色在剧情中段死亡，这样观众就不能想当然的认为人气角色就一定可以幸存到大结局。在被问到某个角色非死不可的原因时，大卫·西蒙回答道：<blockquote>这部电视剧里，我们既不是在散播希望，也不想取悦观众，更不是要贩卖廉价的胜利。《火线》是要讨论群体——官僚机构、犯罪组织、毒品文化、资本主义对个人的影响。它并不是纯粹的娱乐品。我恐怕得说，这是部或多或少表达愤怒的电视剧<ref>{{cite web 
 |author=David Simon 
 |year=2003 
 |title=David Simon Answers Fans' Questions 
 |publisher=[[HBO|HBO]] 
 |language=en 
 |accessdate= 
 |url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/interviews/index.html 
 |deadurl=no 
 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20031204070427/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/interviews/index.html 
 |archivedate=2003-12-04 
 }}</ref>。</blockquote>

=== 主要角色 ===
==== 第一季：法律方和巴克斯戴尔团伙 ====
《火线》的主要角色分为法律方（警察、检察官、法官）和巴克斯戴尔团伙（毒贩）。对巴克斯戴尔团伙的调查因警探吉米·麦克纳提（Jimmy McNulty，[[多米尼克·韦斯特|多米尼克·韦斯特]]饰演)而起 。麦克纳提不服从上级指挥，又受到酗酒和婚姻问题的困扰，但是他富于才干<ref name="West profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/dominic_west.shtml|language=en|title=Cast & Crew - Dominic West as Jimmy McNulty|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080129045438/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/dominic_west.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-29}}</ref><ref name="McNulty profile">{{cite web|year = 2006|language = en|title = Character profile - Jimmy McNulty|publisher = HBO|accessdate = 2007-12-19|url = http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/jimmy_mcnulty.shtml|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071211232901/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/jimmy_mcnulty.shtml|archivedate = 2007-12-11}}</ref>。调查小组由中队长塞德里克·丹尼尔斯（Cedric Daniels，[[兰斯·雷迪克|兰斯·雷迪克]]饰演) 领导，但他一直在希望今后平步青云还是当下专心办案的选择间权衡<ref name="Reddick profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/lance_reddick.shtml|language=en|title=Cast & Crew - Lance Reddick as Cedric Daniels|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080129233603/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/lance_reddick.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-29}}</ref><ref name="Daniels profile">{{cite web|year = 2006|language = en|title = Character profile - Lieutenant Cedric Daniels|publisher = HBO|accessdate = 2007-12-19|url = http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/cedric_daniels.shtml|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071229093546/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/cedric_daniels.shtml|archivedate = 2007-12-29}}</ref>。基玛·格雷戈斯（Kima Greggs，{{link-en|宋雅·孙|Sonja Sohn}}饰演）是一位能力出众的警探，但她既受到同事的嫉妒，又要平复女友对其人身安全的担忧<ref name="Sohn profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/sonja_sohn.shtml|language=en|title=Cast & Crew - Sonja Sohn as Shakima "Kima" Greggs|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080115074259/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/sonja_sohn.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-15}}</ref><ref name="Greggs Profile">{{cite web|language = en|year = 2006|title = Character profile - Detective Shakima "Kima" Greggs|publisher = HBO|accessdate = 2007-12-19|url = http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/kima_greggs.shtml|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071230084158/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/kima_greggs.shtml|archivedate = 2007-12-30}}</ref>。她的调查很大程度上依靠[[线人|线人]]——吸毒者巴伯斯（Bubbles，{{link-en|安德烈·罗伊|Andre Royo}}饰演）的协助<ref name="Royo profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/andre_royo.shtml|language=en|title=Cast & Crew - Andre Royo as Bubbles|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080120073430/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/andre_royo.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-20}}</ref><ref name="Bubbles profile">{{cite web|year = 2006|language = en|title = Character profile - Bubbles|publisher = HBO|accessdate = 2007-12-19|url = http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/bubbles.shtml|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071218155727/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/bubbles.shtml|archivedate = 2007-12-18}}</ref>。托马斯·豪克（Thomas "Herc" Hauk，外号“赫克”，[[多米尼克·伦巴多兹|多米尼克·伦巴多兹]]饰演）和伊利斯·卡佛（Ellis Carver，[[塞思·吉列姆|塞思·吉列姆]]饰演）与格雷戈斯一样，都是从缉毒处抽调到调查组的<ref name="Gilliam profile">{{Cite web|language=en|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/seth_gilliam.shtml|title=Cast & Crew - Seth Gilliam as Ellis Carver|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080106081227/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/seth_gilliam.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-06}}</ref><ref name="Lombardozzi profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/domenick_lombardozzi.shtml|language=en|title=Cast & Crew - Domenick Lombardozzi as Thomas "Herc" Hauk|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080129224621/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/domenick_lombardozzi.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-29}}</ref>。这对搭档最终收敛了自己的暴力天性，在监视工作中大放异彩，且不时为观众带来笑料<ref name="Salon">{{cite web 
