 }}</ref><ref name="Carver profile">{{cite web|year = 2006|language = en|title = Character profile - Ellis Carver|publisher = HBO|accessdate = 2007-12-19|url = http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/ellis_carver.shtml|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071211232856/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/ellis_carver.shtml|archivedate = 2007-12-11}}</ref><ref name="Herc profile">{{cite web|year = 2006|language = en|title = Character profile - Thomas "Herc" Hauk|publisher = HBO|accessdate = 2007-12-19|url = http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/herc_hauk.shtml|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071230090714/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/herc_hauk.shtml|archivedate = 2007-12-30}}</ref>。来到临时调查组的还有警探莱斯特·福瑞蒙（Lester Freamon，[[克拉克·彼得斯|克拉克·彼得斯]]饰演）和诺兰德·普兰兹兰斯基（Roland "Prez" Pryzbylewski，外号“普兰兹”，[[吉姆·特魯-福斯特|吉姆·特魯-福斯特]]饰演）<ref name="Peters profile">{{Cite web|language=en|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/clarke_peters.shtml|title=Cast & Crew - Clarke Peters as Lester Freamon|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080115074244/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/clarke_peters.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-15}}</ref><ref name="True-Frost profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/jim_truefrost.shtml|title=Cast & Crew - Jim True-Frost as Roland "Prez" Pryzbylewski|accessdate=2008-01-15|language=en|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080129224626/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/jim_truefrost.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-29}}</ref>。福瑞蒙尽管在执行行动时并非骨干，但却长于发现看似微不足道却意义非凡的线索<ref name="Freamon profile">{{cite web|year = 2006|language = en|title = Character profile - Lester Freamon|publisher = HBO|accessdate = 2007-12-19|url = http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/lester_freamon.shtml|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071229093638/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/lester_freamon.shtml|archivedate = 2007-12-29}}</ref>；普兰兹则擅长解迷和文件追踪<ref name = "Prez profile">{{cite web|year = 2006|language = en|title = Character profile - Roland "Prez" Pryzbylewski|publisher = HBO|accessdate = 2007-12-19|url = http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/prez.shtml}}</ref>。

这些警员的工作受到上司——区警长威廉·瑞尔斯（William Rawls，{{link-en|约翰·多曼|John Doman}}饰演）和局长艾尔文·巴瑞尔（Ervin Burrell，[[弗兰基·费森|弗兰基·费森]]饰演）监督，但两人关心并非案件的侦破进展，而是政治和个人的仕途<ref name="Faison profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/frankie_r_faison.shtml|language=en|title=Cast & Crew - Frankie R. Faison as Ervin Burrell|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071229151448/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/frankie_r_faison.shtml|archivedate=2007-12-29}}</ref><ref name="Burrell profile">{{cite web|year = 2006|language = en|title = Character profile - Ervin Burrell|publisher = HBO|accessdate = 2007-12-19|url = http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/ervin_burrell.shtml|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071229093626/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/ervin_burrell.shtml|archivedate = 2007-12-29}}</ref><ref name="Doman profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/john_doman.shtml|language=en|title=Cast & Crew - John Doman as William Rawls|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080129233558/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/john_doman.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-29}}</ref><ref name="Rawls profile">{{cite web|year = 2006|language = en|title = Character profile - William Rawls|publisher = HBO|accessdate = 2007-12-19|url = http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/william_rawls.shtml|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071214031018/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/william_rawls.shtml|archivedate = 2007-12-14}}</ref>。州助理检察官伦达·珀尔曼（Rhonda Pearlman， {{link-en|迪尔德·洛夫乔伊|Deirdre Lovejoy}}饰演）负责专案组和法官之间的联络工作，她曾与麦克纳提发生过关系<ref name="Lovejoy profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/deirdre_lovejoy.shtml|title=Cast & Crew - Deirdre Lovejoy as Rhonda Pearlman|accessdate=2008-01-15|language=en|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080104084432/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/deirdre_lovejoy.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-04}}</ref><ref name="Pearlman profile">{{cite web|year = 2006|language = en|title = Character profile - Rhonda Pearlman|publisher = HBO|accessdate = 2007-12-19|url = http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/rhonda_pearlman.shtml|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071211232906/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/rhonda_pearlman.shtml|archivedate = 2007-12-11}}</ref>。在凶杀调查部门，麦克纳提的搭档邦克·莫兰德（Bunk Moreland，{{link-en|温德·皮尔斯|Wendell Pierce}}饰演）是一位出色的警探。他们的上司是警督杰·兰兹曼（Sergeant Jay Landsman，{{link-en|德莱尼·威廉姆斯|Delaney Williams}}饰演）<ref name="Landsman profile" /><ref name="Pierce profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/wendell_pierce.shtml|language=en|title=Cast & Crew - Wendell Pierce as William "Bunk" Moreland|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080115074304/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/wendell_pierce.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-15}}</ref><ref name="Bunk profile">{{cite web|year = 2006|language = en|title = Character profile - Bunk Moreland|publisher = HBO|accessdate = 2007-12-19|url = http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/bunk_moreland.shtml|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071213171005/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/bunk_moreland.shtml|archivedate = 2007-12-13}}</ref><ref name="Delaney Williams profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/delaney_williams.shtml|title=Cast & Crew - Delaney Williams as Jay Landsman|language=en|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080104084437/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/delaney_williams.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-04}}</ref>。{{link-en|彼得格雷蒂|Peter Gerety}}在剧中饰演法官费兰，正是在他的要求下，该案的调查才开始的<ref name = "Salon"/>。

调查对象是以伊旺·巴克斯戴尔（Avon Barksdale，[[伍德·哈瑞斯|伍德·哈瑞斯]]饰演）为首的贩毒组织。他的智囊是斯丁格·贝尔（Stringer Bell，[[伊德瑞斯·艾尔巴|伊德瑞斯·艾尔巴]]饰演）<ref name="Harris profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/avon_barksdale.shtml|title=Cast & Crew - Wood Harris as Avon Barksdale|accessdate=2008-01-15|language=en|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080111164537/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/avon_barksdale.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-11}}</ref><ref name="Avon profile">{{cite web|year = 2006|title = Character profile - Avon Barksdale|publisher = HBO|language = en|accessdate = 2007-12-19|url = http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/avon_barksdale.shtml|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071215124429/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/avon_barksdale.shtml|archivedate = 2007-12-15}}</ref><ref name="Elba profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/idris_elba.shtml|language=en|title=Cast & Crew - Idris Elba as Stringer Bell|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080120073435/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/idris_elba.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-20}}</ref><ref name="Stringer profile">{{cite web|year = 2006|language = en|title = Character profile - Stringer Bell|publisher = HBO|accessdate = 2007-12-19|url = http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/stringer_bell.shtml|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071230002641/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/stringer_bell.shtml|archivedate = 2007-12-30}}</ref>。伊旺的外甥迪安吉拉·巴克斯戴尔（D'Angelo Barksdale，{{link-en|小拉里·吉尔兰德|Larry Gilliard Jr.}}饰演）协助舅舅运作部分地区的毒品交易，但始终抱有负罪感<ref name="Gilliard profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/larry_gilliard.shtml|title=Cast & Crew - Larry Gilliard, Jr. as D'Angelo Barksdale|language=en|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080104084442/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/larry_gilliard.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-04}}</ref><ref name="D profile">{{cite web|year = 2006|title = Character profile - D'Angelo Barksdale|language = en|publisher = HBO|accessdate = 2007-12-19|url = http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/dangelo_barksdale.shtml|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071220233123/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/dangelo_barksdale.shtml|archivedate = 2007-12-20}}</ref>；忠实的手下威毕·布瑞斯（Wee-Bey Brice，{{link-en|哈桑·约翰逊|Hassan Johnson}}）曾在伊旺的授意下进行了多次谋杀<ref name="Hassan Johnson profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/hassan_johnson.shtml|language=en|title=Cast & Crew - Hassan Johnson as Roland "Wee-Bey" Brice|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080129131009/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/hassan_johnson.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-29}}</ref><ref name="Wee-Bey profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/weebey.shtml|language=en|title=Character profile - Roland "Wee-Bey" Brice|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080121195932/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/weebey.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-21}}</ref>。在迪安吉拉手下工作的街头毒贩有普特·卡尔（Poot Carr，{{link-en|崔·钱尼|Tray Chaney}}饰演）、博迪·布罗德斯（Bodie Broadus ，[[J·D·威廉姆斯|J·D·威廉姆斯]]饰演）以及瓦伦斯（Wallace，[[迈克尔·B·乔丹|迈克尔·B·乔丹]]饰演）<ref name = "Salon"/><ref name="Chaney profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/tray_chaney.shtml|language=en|title=Cast & Crew - Tray Chaney as Malik "Poot" Carr|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080104084522/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/tray_chaney.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-04}}</ref><ref name="JD Williams profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/jd_williams.shtml|language=en|title=Cast & Crew - JD Williams as Preston "Bodie" Broadus|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080129045443/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/jd_williams.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-29}}</ref>。瓦伦斯是一个聪明、有些天真的少年，受环境所迫从事毒品交易<ref name = "Salon"/>；普特是个粗人，比起担任领导者，他更乐意追随他人<ref name="Poot profile">{{cite web|year = 2006|title = Character profile - Malik "Poot" Carr|publisher = HBO|accessdate = 2007-12-19|url = http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/poot.shtml|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071215033150/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/poot.shtml|archivedate = 2007-12-15}}</ref>。奥马·利特（Omar Little，[[迈克·肯尼斯·威廉姆斯|迈克·肯尼斯·威廉姆斯]]饰演）以抢劫毒贩为生，常常侵犯到巴克斯戴尔团伙的利益<ref name="MK Williams profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/michael_k_williams.shtml|language=en|title=Cast & Crew - Michael Kenneth Williams as Omar Little|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080126091555/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/michael_k_williams.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-26}}</ref><ref name="Omar profile">{{cite web|year = 2006|title = Character profile - Omar Little|language = en|publisher = HBO|accessdate = 2007-12-19|url = http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/omar.shtml|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071230001007/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/omar.shtml|archivedate = 2007-12-30}}</ref>。

==== 第二季：码头方 ====
