iveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080110111043/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/beatrice_russell.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-10}}</ref>；索伯塔是工会领导人，为了筹钱拯救自己领导的工会，不得不从事犯罪活动<ref name="Frank Sobotka profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/port/frank_sobotka.shtml|language=en|title=Character profile - Frank Sobotka|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080102233528/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/port/frank_sobotka.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-02}}</ref>。在第二季中加入的新角色还有弗兰克的侄子尼克·索伯塔（Nick Sobotka，[[帕伯罗·施赖伯|帕伯罗·施赖伯]]饰演）<ref name="Schreiber profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/port/pablo_schreiber.shtml|title=Cast & Crew - Pablo Schreiber as Nick Sobotka|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080129230129/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/port/pablo_schreiber.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-29}}</ref><ref name="Nick Sobotka profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/port/nick_sobotka.shtml|title=Character profile - Nick Sobotka|language=en|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080115074320/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/port/nick_sobotka.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-15}}</ref>、弗兰克之子雷吉·索伯塔（Ziggy Sobotka，[[詹姆斯·冉森|詹姆斯·冉森]]饰演）<ref name="Ransone profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/port/james_ransone.shtml|title=Cast & Crew - James Ransone as Ziggy Sobotka|language=en|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080129233618/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/port/james_ransone.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-29}}</ref><ref name="Ziggy profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/port/ziggy_sobotka.shtml|title=Character profile - Ziggy|language=en|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080103000522/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/port/ziggy_sobotka.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-03}}</ref>以及旺达斯的神秘老板“希腊人”（"The Greek"，{{link-en|比尔·雷蒙德|Bill Raymond}}饰演）<ref name="Raymond profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/port/bill_raymond.shtml|title=Cast & Crew - Bill Raymond as The Greek|language=en|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080129230124/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/port/bill_raymond.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-29}}</ref><ref name="Greek profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/port/the_greek.shtml|title=Character profile - The Greek|language=en|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080128175559/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/port/the_greek.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-28}}</ref>。第二季之后，港口不再是剧情重点，这些新角色也就淡出了。

==== 第三季：政客方和斯坦菲尔德团伙 ====
第三季部分曾出镜的角色回归，形成了庞大的常规演出阵容，其中包括警探林德·西德诺（Leander Sydnor，{{link-en|科瑞·帕克·罗宾逊|Corey Parker Robinson}}饰演）<ref name="Parker Robinson profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/corey_parker_robinson.shtml|language=en|title=Cast & Crew - Corey Parker Robinson as Leander Sydnor|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080110111033/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/corey_parker_robinson.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-10}}</ref>、博迪<ref name="JD Williams profile"/>、奥马<ref name="MK Williams profile"/>、乔·史都华（Proposition Joe Stewart，{{link-en|罗伯特·F·楚|Robert F. Chew}}饰演）<ref name="Robert F. Chew profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/robert_f_chew.shtml|title=Cast & Crew - Robert F. Chew as Proposition Joe Stewart|language=en|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080129233627/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/robert_f_chew.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-29}}</ref>以及区警长霍华德·考文（Howard "Bunny" Colvin，{{link-en|罗伯特·维斯德姆|Robert Wisdom}}）<ref name="Wisdom profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/robert_wisdom.shtml|title=Cast & Crew - Robert Wisdom as Howard "Bunny" Colvin|language=en|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080104084506/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/robert_wisdom.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-04}}</ref>。考文负责管理巴克斯戴尔团伙盘踞的西区，他在临近退休之际决定采取激进的办法解决毒品问题<ref name="Colvin profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/bunny_colvin.shtml|title=Character profile - Howard "Bunny" Colvin|accessdate=2008-01-15|language=en|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080118124333/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/bunny_colvin.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-18}}</ref>。东区的毒枭乔·史都华转变态度，同意跟巴克斯戴尔团伙合作<ref name="Prop Joe profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/prop_joe.shtml|title=Character profile - Proposition Joe Stewart|accessdate=2008-01-15|language=en|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080128175605/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/prop_joe.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-28}}</ref>。第一季中前途无量的警察局新星林德·西德诺（Leander Sydnor）在本季作为重案组成员重新出镜<ref name="Sydnor profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/leander_sydnor.shtml|title=Character profile - Leander Sydnor|accessdate=2008-01-15|language=en|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080101020159/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/leander_sydnor.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-01}}</ref>。博迪在巴克斯戴尔团伙中逐渐得到重用，他对毒品贸易有与生俱来的禀赋<ref name="Bodie profile">{{cite web|year = 2006|title = Character profile - Preston "Bodie" Broadus|language = en|publisher = HBO|accessdate = 2007-12-19|url = http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/bodie.shtml|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071206145933/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/bodie.shtml|archivedate = 2007-12-06}}</ref>。奥马和巴克斯戴尔团伙的深仇未解，前者常常给予后者沉重打击<ref name = "Omar profile"/>。

