://web.archive.org/web/20080127162509/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/namond_brice.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-27}}</ref><ref name="Michael profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/michael_lee.shtml|title=Character profile - Michael Lee|language=en|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080118125702/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/michael_lee.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-18}}</ref><ref name="Randy profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/randy_wagstaff.shtml|title=Character profile - Randy Wagstaff|language=en|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080127162514/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/randy_wagstaff.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-27}}</ref><ref name="Dukie profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/duquan_dukie_weems.shtml|title=Character profile - Duquan "Dukie" Weems|language=en|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080124183324/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/duquan_dukie_weems.shtml|archivedate=2008-01-24}}</ref>。另一个新角色是卡瑟提的代理竞选主管诺曼·威尔森（Norman Wilson，{{link-en|瑞吉·E·凯西|Reg E. Cathey}}饰演）<ref name="Cathey profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/reg_cathey.shtml|title=Cast & Crew - Reg E. Cathey as Norman Wilson|language=en|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071229151552/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/actors/reg_cathey.shtml|archivedate=2007-12-29}}</ref><ref name="Wilson profile">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/norman_wilson.shtml|title=Character profile - Norman Wilson|language=en|accessdate=2008-01-15|publisher=HBO|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071229093703/http://www.hbo.com/thewire/cast/characters/norman_wilson.shtml|archivedat