== 反响 ==
=== 评论 ===
第一季得到了评论界的正面评价<ref name="TCA">{{cite web |title = Television Critics Association Introduces 2003 Award Nominees |accessdate =  |publisher = Television Critics Association |url = http://tvcritics.org/press/2003/06/television-critics-association.html |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061013052704/http://tvcritics.org/press/2003/06/television-critics-association.html |archivedate = 2006-10-13 |deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title = The Wire: The Complete First Season|publisher = Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate = |language = en|url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wire_the_complete_first_season/?show=all|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20050114051301/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wire_the_complete_first_season/?show=all|archivedate = 2005-01-14|deadurl = no}}</ref>，部分评论甚至认为该剧超越了《[[黑道家族|黑道家族]]》和《[[六呎风云|六英尺下]]》这些HBO知名的“旗舰”剧情剧<ref>{{cite news|author = Alan Sepinwall|language = en|year = 2006|title = Taut 'Wire' has real strength.|page = 1|publisher = Newark Star-Ledger|date = 2006-08-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author = Aaron Barnhart|year = 2006|title = 'The Wire' aims higher: TV's finest hour is back|publisher = Kansas City Star|language = en|accessdate = |url = http://www.kansascity.com/mld/kansascity/entertainment/columnists/aaron_barnhart/15410184.htm|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070109194816/http://www.kansascity.com/mld/kansascity/entertainment/columnists/aaron_barnhart/15410184.htm|archivedate = 2007-01-09|deadurl = no}}[http://web.archive.org/web/*/http://www.kansascity.com/mld/kansascity/entertainment/columnists/aaron_barnhart/15410184.htm web.archive]</ref><ref>{{cite web|author = Leslie Ryan|year = 2003|title = Tapping ''The Wire''; HBO Police Drama Tops Television Week's Semiannual Critics Poll List|language = en|publisher = Television Week|accessdate = |url = http://www.findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_go2037/is_200307/ai_n8968965|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924013135/http://www.findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_go2037/is_200307/ai_n8968965|archivedate = 2015-09-24}}</ref>。有评论认为，尽管该剧在主题上仍受到HBO及大卫·西蒙早期作品的桎梏，但仍然值得一看，并称该剧对禁毒战争的描写影射了反恐战争，很能引起观众共鸣<ref name="BP1">{{cite web|author = Robert David Sullivan|year = 2002|title = Slow Hand|publisher = Boston Phoenix|language = en|accessdate = |url = http://www.bostonphoenix.com/boston/arts/tv/documents/02394694.htm|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071012185239/http://bostonphoenix.com/boston/arts/tv/documents/02394694.htm|archivedate = 2007-10-12}}</ref>。也有评论认为该剧依赖于阴谋论调且剧情发展缓慢，很可能会命运多舛，但对剧中的人物刻画以及犯罪阴谋还是持肯定态度的<ref name="TMD">{{cite web|author = Todd Weiser|year = 2002|title = New HBO series ''The Wire'' taps into summer programming|publisher = The Michigan Daily|language = en|accessdate = |url = http://www.michigandaily.com/media/storage/paper851/news/2002/06/17/Arts/New-Hbo.Series.the.Wire.Taps.Into.Summer.Programming-1411494.shtml|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070930185112/http://www.michigandaily.com/media/storage/paper851/news/2002/06/17/Arts/New-Hbo.Series.the.Wire.Taps.Into.Summer.Programming-1411494.shtml|archivedate = 2007-09-30|deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

